 1998-16321998-09-150,  ,  HERITAGE,  , 
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ART W. MAY, of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Daniel Haughn, whose term has expired.
